headline: TOBLERONE® Introduces the Crown Jewel of the Holiday Season
summary: Just in time for the holiday season, TOBLERONE unveils the latest addition to its "Never Square" line of premium chocolates: TOBLERONE Truffles. These luxurious truffles are a gem-sized version of the classic taste of TOBLERONE. Each individually wrapped truffle is great for delighting the chocolate lover in your life with a sophisticated milk chocolate treat or indulging in a moment to yourself amidst the holiday hustle.
